  "title": "L1/L2 Certified Childcare Chinese Language Teacher - EH03",
  "description": "<h2><strong>L1/L2 Certified Childcare Chinese Language Teacher</strong></h2><p><strong>Location:</strong> Boon Keng, Raffles place, Novena<br /><strong>(Islandwide centers available)</strong><br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5 days, 8am-6pm<br /><strong>Salary:</strong> $3200-$4300</p><h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Teach Mandarin language to children</p></li><li><p>Plan and implement class programme according to centre’s framework</p></li><li><p>Prepare progress reports and developmental portfolios each semester</p></li><li><p>Create a stimulating learning environment</p></li><li><p>Manage classroom and perform routine care duties</p></li><li><p>Ensure children’s safety and hygiene</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with other teaching staff</p></li><li><p>Communicate with parents on child development</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p><p>Minimum Diploma in Early Childhood Care and Education (DECCE)</p></p><p><p>ECDA Certified at L1/L2 category<br /></p></p><p>✅Interested personnel kindly send your CV to WhatsApp: https://wa.me/65 88567364(Ethan)</p><p>Han Meng Zhuo | Reg No: R25138931</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</p><p><br /></p>",
